summary:
I’m full of energy, resourceful, and always looking to learn and develop myself. 

As a Social Science and Entrepreneurship graduate, I am driven to build impactful solutions for a better tomorrow. What excites me in this journey is using my analytical, communication and innovative capabilities to develop strategic tailored solutions and nurture collaborative relationships. I have experience in business development, marketing, market research, sustainability, public relations, content creation, entrepreneurship and qualitative fieldwork.

In my quest to learn, I always look to connect with mentors and professionals who are willing to share their experiences and opportunities. I would love to connect with you here on LinkedIn or over coffee ☕️ !
